lead_paragraph: Chris Wondolowski scored on a penalty kick and David Bingham had five saves to help the San Jose Earthquakes beat Sporting Kansas City 1-0 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Bingham, Wondolowski Lead Quakes Past Sporting KC, 1-0
